Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred added 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3459] nothing converted to string should return nothing and not fail
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3457] add addition characters that can be hard to work with in nushell
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3451] updated round to support i64
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3439] updated to the latest rustyline
, and 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3438] don't let externals break ansi escapes
, and 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3429] re-enable ansi support when externals break it
jonathandturner did 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3455] a bit more cleanup of block params
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3453] split unit into duration and filesize
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3452] changed to paren interpolation
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3450] improved block params
, 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3444] added explicit block params
, and did a fix to 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3442] treat u64 like i64 for now
kubouch 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3449] removed rest_args() from evaluated CommandArgs
, and 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3441] fixed path join argument type and a typo
elferherrera added the ability to 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3437] load parquet and json files
, moved 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3426] commands to engine p
, and 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3425] added new dataframe commands
schrieveslaach 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3432] added Support for Partial Completions
alexshadley 
[link: https://api.github.com/repos/nushell/nushell/issues/3427] added negative indexing for range
